Requirments: Docket Desktop app.

Clonning the project from the branch:
git clone --branch docker https://github.com/hamamiMaestro/FinalProject-Afeka.git

After cloning the project, run the Docker app and open terminal:
1. cd ProjectCode
2. docker-compose up -d --build
3. Open browser with the url https://localhost:8000/
3.1. If the page doesn't load open the file settings.py in "/ProjectCode/sql_training/settings.py" with text editor -> change CRLF -> LF
     Do the same change for "/ProjectCode/scripts/entrypoint.sh" file
4. The browser will detect our keys and will display warning message, click "Advance" -> "Proceed to localhost (unsafe)"
